<br>
To GoL, its okay (justified and ethical) to roll on loot that's on a mob you didn't kill while the guild that killed it is standing next to the corpse. <br>
<br>
To GoL, its not okay (unjustified and unethical) for the guild that killed that same mob, to use the /petition feature of the game to report those actions when its a &quot;No Drop&quot; item. <br>
<br>
<br>
